text: The Very Rev Wendy Mary Callan Open Charities was Dean of Killala from 2012 to 2013.Diocese of Tuam web site Callan was born in 1952, educated at Oxford Brookes University and ordained in 2000. After a curacy in Bicester she was Vicar of Shipton-under-Wychwood from 2003 until 2010. In that year she became the incumbent at Kilmoremoy.Sligo Champion ==Notes== Category:1952 births Category:21st-century Anglican priests Category:Living people Category:Deans of Killala Category:Alumni of Oxford Brookes University
